p: Although the symptoms of ZIKV among other arboviruses are very similar, the analyses showed that in the years 2015 and 2016, among 146 suspected ZIKV cases, two symptoms were the most frequent: rash occurred in 99 (67.8%) in 2015 and 614 (79.0 %) in 2016 and pruritus occurred in 93 (63.7%) in 2015 and 549 (70.7%) in 2016.
